    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In n(omine) D(omi)ni. Constat me <persName key="#Deacons #Abbots #Monks"
                            ref="#people/1554">Andreas</persName> gr(aci)a D(e)i <rs key="#Deacons"
                            >diacon(us)</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> atq(ue) <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abb(as)</rs> regul(e) <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >mon(asterii)</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money #Monasteries #Deacons #Abbots #Monks"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1487">S(an)c(t)i Apolenaris q(ui) v(ocatur)
                            Novo</orgName> accepissem et accepi at vob(is) <persName><name
                                ref="Apollinaris">Apolenaris</name></persName> filio q(uo)nd(am)
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Ioh(anni)s</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Rent_in_money">pensione(m)</rs> p(ro) tres <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">uncias</rs> in int(egro) q(ui) est posita in
                            <rs key="#Fundi">fundu(m)</rs> qui vocat(ur) <geogName
                            key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money"><placeName
                                key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money"
                                >Colopedio</placeName></geogName> cu(m) om(n)ib(us) sibi
                        p(er)tinentib(us), territorio <geogName key="#Fundi #Fines"><placeName
                                key="#Fundi #Fines" ref="#places/3515"
                            >Liv(iense)</placeName></geogName>, <rs key="#Plebs">pl(ebe)</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1488">S(an)c(t)e
                            Reparate</orgName>, quas p(er) <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >enfiteosin</rs> tenere viso estis at iure sup(er)scripti mon(asterii)
                        n(ost)ri, p(ro) indicionib(us) transactis usq(ue) in ista pressente quinta
                        [et] p(er) [un]aqua(m)q(ue) indictione den(arii) q(ui)nq(ue) tantu(m). Unde
                        p(ro) munimine v(est)ro feci vob(is) [u]nc deaccepto in m(en)se marcio,
                        indiccione q(ui)nta, <placeName ref="#places/594">Rav(enne)</placeName>.
                        [A]ndreas di(a)c(onus) et mon(achus) et abba mon(a)s(terii) S(an)c(t)i
                        Polenaris in oc deaccepto s(ub)s(cripsi).</ab>
